text: Kavango East is a region in Namibia. The capital is Rundu. The region was created in 2013, when the Kavango Region was split into Kavango East and Kavango West. The region has the western half of the Caprivi Strip. There are 6 constituencies: * Mashare * Mukwe * Ndiyona * Ndonga Linena * Rundu Rural * Rundu Urban Category:2013 establishments in Namibia Category:Regions of Namibia
